# Sample environment file for tests.
# Printing is browser-direct (Web Bluetooth + WebUSB) — no print-server,
# no test-mode flags needed. Tests that exercise printing should mock the
# driver itself (e.g. spy on BluetoothUniversalPrinter.print).

# Supabase (replace with test-project credentials)
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=...
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=...
